title: PM Modi Nepal Visit Live: Feel blessed, says Modi on visit to Maya Devi temple, lays foundation stone of Buddhist Centre - The Indian Express
content: PM Modi Nepal Visit Live: Feel blessed, says Modi on visit to Maya Devi temple, lays foundation stone of Buddhist Centre  The Indian ExpressView Full coverage on Google News
description: PM Modi in Nepal Live Updates: "Happy to be among the wonderful people of Nepal on the special occasion of Buddha Purnima. Looking forward to the programmes in Lumbini," PM Modi tweeted.
